{
  "stem": "26728.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And of course-- and-- and we were told, you know, like I said, these are-- these-- these guys were on their way out, the way he put it.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And the smell was-- it just permeated your pores.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "You could just, and I had a flat leather flight jacket on, like that one in that picture.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Uh, and it just went-- you know-- uh, it didn't make you sick.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I never did get nauseated.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I got very angry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I became very angry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Uh, I-- I-- [SIGHS] and I'll tell you some more about that later.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I-- OK, we-- we saw all the bodies.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "We saw interviewed, some of these-- or met with some of these, this one rabbi, and some of these college guys, professors who spoke English.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh he was--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was very lucid.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was very thin, uh, emaciated.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Uh, but he survived.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "These colleagues, they had-- they had-- they took care of each other.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Uh, they had an organization and they would-- they took care of the weak ones and the important ones.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The other inmates made sacrifices.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "If a person had typhus and they knew he was going to die, or they felt he was going to die, they made a deal with him just to take his rations and give it to somebody else.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I went through the whole thing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was-- And it was a typical army type mess hall, but there was no food there in-- in Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, you know, there was some bread and some big vats of-- what soup.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I suppose you could call it that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But there were turnips.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And-- And, um, I never saw any meat at Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we went through the warehouses, too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But they had stripped-- you see, the SS had split.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
